name: apm_sa3_2016_timeseries
title: APM - Timeseries Property Data (SA3) 01/03/1994 - 31/01/2021
abstract:
This dataset describes for sale, for rent listings and sold property data across Australia for the period 01/03/1994 - 31/01/2021. Each data point represents an aggregation of 12 months' worth of data and is reported monthly. It follows the Australian Statistical Geography Standard (ASGS) 2016 Statistical Area Level 3 (SA3) boundaries.

For Sale/For Rent listings are available from 2003 for all states. APM sold data are available from: NSW, SA, QLD, ACT, WA since 1993, auction results in Sydney since 1989, VIC since 1985, NT since 1998 and TAS since 2003.

AURIN has spatially enabled the original data.
